ggttttyy() -- System Call (libc)

Device-dependent control
#iinncclluuddee <ssggttttyy.hh>
iinntt ggttttyy(_f_d, _s_g_p)
iinntt _f_d; ssttrruucctt ssggttttyybb *_s_g_p;

ggttttyy() gets  attributes of a terminal.  It is  shorthand notation for iiooccttll
calls with a _c_o_m_m_a_n_d argument of TTIIOOCCGGEETTPP.

_E_x_a_m_p_l_e
For examples of this system call, see ppiippee() and ssttttyy().

_S_e_e _A_l_s_o
